{"type": "article", "id": 50072, "title": "混凝土做的吊灯，像向日葵花盘一样精巧｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-02-08T23:21:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 2629, "name": "HAY"}, {"id": 47672, "name": "Maxdesign"}, {"id": 47673, "name": "ARDOMA Design"}, {"id": 24001, "name": "Zero"}, {"id": 24002, "name": "Front"}, {"id": 47674, "name": "Esrawe Studio"}, {"id": 47675, "name": "Tomás Alonso"}, {"id": 34339, "name": "Dror Kaspi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180208201411FXHnUmroK95L6wuM.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #638c0b; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #638c0b} span.s7 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Dolmen Collection by Esrawe Studio</h3><p>墨西哥设计工作室 Esrawe 在本周的 Zona Maco 艺术博览会上第一次推出了家具系列 Dolmen，包含一系列核桃木、黑胡桃木的餐桌餐椅设计，另有一套轻质白橡木座椅。</p><p>设计师 Héctor Esrawe 表示：“Dolmen 系列是对不同材质的元素之间的平衡的探索。”餐具柜和餐桌都配有黑色大理石底座支撑的木质桌面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201444eTJHDamKhS5oVMrL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.451777\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201446FnjroEeaRLV5pMzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802082014499blh8AuQjBESytrw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201449BIgGYP3Z5bE0AVLK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.459391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201450wObJTsWDk3q0jEVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201450AsztpPQYZGyueHkq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hoop by Front for Zero</h3><p>斯德哥尔摩工作室 Front 为设计品牌 Zero 创造了一系列灯具 Hoop，其特点是颜色鲜艳的金属丝灯罩。特别的笼状结构，有一系列或明亮或柔和的色彩，八根钢丝构成的椭圆形笼子，好似轻轻地托着灯球。电线隐藏在笼子内侧，连接到玻璃灯底部，刻意营造出笼子和玻璃灯完全断开的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201658dYGm1gwU3C0cQMBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201658pB6rQIqS49dvu0Ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201658WUzxuMKOdSPNVTe5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201658UecOazFJKCw0NhjS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.328257\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201658ufilXGAdmNBr2Ox6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.328257\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201658FhZaT4wRSQpX3gv8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hear Us Out by Students from Beckmans College of Design</h3><p>瑞典贝克曼斯设计学院的 12 名学生与 6 个瑞典品牌 Blå Station、Gärsnäs、Johanson Design、Källemo、Massproductions 和 Materia 合作，在今年的斯德哥尔摩家具展上推出了名为 Hear Us Out 的项目。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201822Af9hF4J7XjaRwB2i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>每个品牌都提出了命题，要求同学们创造出一个适合品牌现有系列的家具作品。</p><p>Ida Björses 和 Celine Strömbäck 为 Blå Station 设计了一款名为 Kaj 的边桌，木材、皮革和金属的混搭，结构精巧，也能用作坐凳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201837XqC7UtZQO2ip9ul5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Lisa Lindh 和 Klara Hedengren 为 Massproductions 设计了一个雕塑般的屏风 Kolonn，由瓦楞纸制成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201910tcbTw19ZPMNfRYz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Vent 椅的设计师是 Sarah Hasselqvist 和 Melinda Urbansdotter，为 Johanson Design 量身而造，灵感源自新鲜的面团，整个椅子就像是柔软的织物随意披在了金属结构上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201923pxI6hVCQjJZa9iyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>受到幸运甜饼启发的 Fortuna 椅，由 Hanna Stenström 和 Jennie Adén 为 Materia 设计，巨大的椅子与甜饼干有相似的形状，中间有一个方形的座位。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208201934NOmJZiWan2GflRe8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Anna Herrmann 和 Lisa Jonsson 为 Gärsnäs 品牌设计了两款凳子，命名为 Fransson，可堆叠的凳子将松木、山毛榉木、胡桃木与皮革和纺织品相结合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802082019474KsfUcxedznIF3EC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Madeleine Nelson 和 Frida Pettersson 被 Källemo 委托使用该公司的材料库创建一个搁架。他们用桦木和铁制造了一个存储系统，也可以作为装饰雕塑使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202004GB0LAYvOlmDsQ6p2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>HELIA Concrete Mesh Light Fixtures by Dror Kaspi for ARDOMA Design</h3><p>由混凝土制成的产品有时会看起来笨拙和粗糙，很少有设计师能够特别精巧地运用这种材料。ARDOMA设计公司的设计师 Dror Kaspi 打算进行新的尝试，HELIA 灯具是个新思路。它具有独特的网状结构，模仿编织纹理，灵感源自向日葵种子图案。为此设计师还开发了一种特殊的混凝土混合物以及新的铸造方法，使光线能够通过其小孔流出。</p><p>HELIA 是吊灯，也可以用作台灯，提供包括浅灰色、深灰色、白色、黄色、蓝色和红色等多种选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202025fqXbtLIAmE5ylgik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838281\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202026YE5qjIuXengoa2W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.568750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202027TutDLZYRV18O0bPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202027vlCVspbhTDESNn2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202027gJolIr9TD8E2dFLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Offset Table by Tomás Alonso for Maxdesign</h3><p>越来越多公司开始引入开放式办公空间的概念，各种具有附加功能的办公桌开始出现，Offset Table 就是其中一种，是设计师 Tomás Alonso 受品牌 Maxdesign 之邀设计的。桌子中心线的空隙，允许桌面隔档的调节，也满足各式电缆、配件以及灯具的管理。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202054bfnOjSDZRLcFhgou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202055iqGNgDpUBcJzkVa9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202055OpUZ6q7AQxBV8JN9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202056EjWFlqvO38iLkcA0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202056U0A4ElfehOpg5oMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202057X8l093tPrHueBZbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>New Order 2.0多元化墙板体系 by HAY</h3><p>New Order 用于适应不断更新的工作环境。Stefan Diez 与 HAY 团队一起，通过增加可定制部分与配件的品种，提升了整个 New Order 系统的功能性及质量。</p><p>最新的部件包含钢门，抽屉和嵌板，这些都可以徒手安装，不需要额外工具辅助，而且可以频繁地日常使用。电缆管理、钣金货架、照明组件、隔板和桌面也有所进化，可适用于特定需求。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z054809rhs8&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202133XGKbEm0LYrNV2pRw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.209375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202133DN26COZnXgrQlhuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.209375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202134JgWFf2asZK48cXmD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202134WvbTaqPVCI0poAYu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.209375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208202135XexOTHFjhbRVM8Y6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.209375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}